Fab Manager

1. introduction
===============

Fab Manager is an open-source application to help fab labs or mackerspaces to run their facility including the following activities:
- Membership
- Equipment
- Material
- Events
- Booking (of equipment...)
- etc...

It includes also an open API that can be activated and allow to join a worldwide network of labs sharing some of their data in order to provide 
global reports.


